刑；致重傷者，處3年以上10年以下有期徒\r\n刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c95%2c20220331%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,交易,95,20220331,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交易","JNO":"95","JDATE":"20220331","JTITLE":"公共危險"}